cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Agent Skills Runtime"
abstract: >-
  A deterministic, binding-driven execution engine for composable AI agent
  skills. Defines agent capabilities as abstract contracts, wires them to
  any backend (Python, OpenAPI, MCP, OpenRPC), and executes multi-step
  workflows as declarative DAGs with built-in safety gates, cognitive state
  tracking, and full observability.
